# Unraid plugin files must ship with LF line endings:
#  - PageBuilder.php splits a .page header from its body on "\n---\n" (pure LF);
#    a CRLF .page fails parse_ini_string and is silently dropped -> no menu entry.
#  - shell shebangs (#!/bin/bash) break on a trailing CR.
# Force LF on every text file regardless of the build host's core.autocrlf.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.png binary
*.ico binary
